Text:
once again I have to congratulate you...you are the best ! Couldn't believe that you were able to post the Starbuck series so quickly. Thank you so much.
If you come across his "thrillers" I would be even more grateful - Wildtrack, Sea Lord, Crackdown, Scoundrel (I've read Stormchild).
Hi, will you be able to get Patrica Cornwell books soon, look great ... thank you for doing this x
